"(define (get-corner lines x-or-y min-or-max)
  (apply min-or-max (for/list ([line lines])
                              (match-let ([(line-spec x1 y1 x2 y2 stroke) line])
                                         (case x-or-y
                                               [(x) (min-or-max x1 x2)]
                                               [(y) (min-or-max y1 y2)])))))"
